.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNEV/111%2c%e5%8d%97%e7%b0%a1%2c380%2c20220421%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNEV,111,南簡,380,20220421,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"南簡","JNO":"380","JDATE":"20220421","JTITLE":"清償借款"}